THE CONFUSION EXPLAINED, PLEASE READ:

There was a torrent uploaded approximately fifteen minutes after the episode aired. It was by an ANONYMOUS uploader using the same title format as ettv and then tacking [ettv] at the end. It was a fake, a rar that required you to do some fishy things to get to the video. OBVIOUSLY it was a scam. That torrent, as far as I can tell, has since been removed. THIS TORRENT was uploaded around an HOUR and fifteen minutes after the episode aired, and has the real, working mp4.

ettv is not at fault, it was the fault of an anonymous scammer who tried to trick the tpb community. It didn't work. However, people are EXTREMELY STUPID and still pin this on ettv.

Thank you, and stop calling this fake. I have it downloaded and have watched it, it is completely legitimate.
